YPInfrastructure
================

Requirements:
    php 5.3
    zip & unzip commands

Installation:
    mkdir ~/.ypi
    cd ~/.ypi
    git clone git://github.com/yonpols/ypinfrastructure.git
    echo 'export PATH=$PATH:~/.ypi/bin' >> ~/.bashrc
    source ~/.bashrc

    Edit php.ini and add /home/user/.ypi/lib
    include_path = .:/home/user/.ypi/lib:....